speacialitites.title: Chicken Karahi
speacialitites.description: Discover the culinary magic of our Chicken Karahi, a symphony of aromatic spices and succulent chicken pieces cooked to perfection. Immerse yourself in the rich, bold flavors of this traditional dish, where the smoky essence of the karahi enhances the natural taste of tender chicken. Each bite is a journey through the heart of Pakistani cuisine

speacialitites.title: Bombay biryani
speacialitites.description: Embark on a culinary journey with our Bombay Biryani, a masterpiece that captures the vibrant essence of Mumbai's street food culture. Immerse yourself in the fragrant aroma of basmati rice layered with tender pieces of marinated meat, aromatic spices, and caramelized onions. The burst of flavors, ranging from savory to slightly tangy

speacialitites.title: Barbeque
speacialitites.description: Ignite your taste buds with the smoky allure of our Barbecue sensation. Succulent cuts of meat, expertly marinated and slow-cooked to perfection, deliver a mouthwatering experience that embodies the essence of outdoor grilling. The savory blend of spices and the charred aroma will transport you to a backyard barbecue paradise

speacialitites.title: Chinese Biryani
speacialitites.description: Savor the fusion in our Chinese Biryani! Fragrant basmati, stir-fried veggies, and tender chicken blend with Chinese spices for a unique culinary experience. Elevate your dining with this delicious crossover!
